<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="A" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Arrant" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Arrant,</orth> arch: <cit><quote>a. knave,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 3.5.35" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado III, 5, 35</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. ado 5.1.330" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 330</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 5.1.35" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B V, 1, 35</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 5.1.35" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B V, 1, 35</bibl> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 5.4.1" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 4, 1</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 1.5.124" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. I, 5, 124</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 3.1.131" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 131</bibl>. <cit><quote>that a. malmsey-nose knave,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 2.1.42" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B II, 1, 42</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a. counterfeit rascal,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 3.6.64" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 III, 6, 64</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a. traitor,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 4.8.10" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV, 8, 10</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a. thief,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tim 4.3.440" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. IV, 3, 440</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a. whore,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lr 2.4.52" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. II, 4, 52</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>a. cowards,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 2.2.106" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A II, 2, 106</bibl></cit>. Fluellen says even: <cit><quote>as a. a piece of knavery,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 4.7.2" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV, 7, 2</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>as a. a villain,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 4.7.2" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 IV, 7, 2</bibl></cit> <cit><quote>what an a., rascally, beggarly, lousy knave it is,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 4.8.36" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 8, 36</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>